%% Diagram: Runtime CSS-in-JS render path vs zero-runtime
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    participant React
    participant Comp as Styled Comp
    participant Lib as Runtime Lib
    participant CSSOM
    participant Layout

    Note over React,Layout: Runtime CSS-in-JS path  every render
    React->>Comp: render(props)
    Comp->>Lib: serialize and interpolate
    Lib->>Lib: hash class name
    Lib->>CSSOM: insert rule
    CSSOM-->>Layout: invalidate styles
    Layout-->>React: recalc plus paint

    Note over React,Layout: Zero-runtime, Modules, Tailwind  no per-render path
    React->>Comp: render(props)
    Comp-->>React: emit className
    Note right of Comp: No serialization or CSSOM mutation
